Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:54.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:00.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:07.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:12.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:26.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:31.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:43.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:53.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:58.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:54.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜歡著緊張的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:00.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}興奮起來走向更廣闊的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:07.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:12.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只專注於眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰都無法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}連同那份淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:26.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:31.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此將宿於手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}盡情揮揚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果斷地  徑直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向著明天全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:43.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在轉瞬即逝之間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}實現那夢中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}無論它多麼虛幻和遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:53.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和僅屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:58.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:11.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第23話\N謊言與沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃  現在只有你一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是大家在等聰莉啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的真要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級就剩下咱倆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  冷清可算是咱們的傳統了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我這個部長再嚴厲一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  大家都因為前次大賽而情緒低落？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為輸掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看咱們部原本不就是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說小珠輸掉比賽是讓我吃了一驚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但昨天也沒什麼特別的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該擔心的是那個對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋啦…你們來啦…繼續吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！快換衣服和我們練習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等人到齊再說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  徹徹底底地洩氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！不就是輸了場比賽  你這算什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這算什麼呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是要被開除嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後比賽還多的是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們把老師的工作找回來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！紀梨乃！真可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說前次大賽是受了不少打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們部現在已經上軌道了！機會有的是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的對手不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒那個鈴木凜的話就沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇…瞧這馬後炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  不動手什麼也不會開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在教室裡找不到自己的眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家一起幫忙找了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠和小都都呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠要值日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都說要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個飾品店嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是店長突然有病所以過去代班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要開始了！快去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不好意思我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要熱身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  我很容易被人打臉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…對方的確打起來很方便…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師  石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長先生找您  請立即到校長室來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為比賽輸了所以要開除嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夠了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  小珠交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後的時間…有這麼漫長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山和…岩佐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像是和外校的學生打架鬥毆後逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有學生受輕傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想讓他們暫時休學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是劍道部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生這種事情還真是棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人說運動部也有連帶責任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個  特別是外山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這個人特別暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有人提出要劍道部休部一年…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！其他的人又沒有責任！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還沒有決定呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太不講理了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個做的事情和劍道部…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道劍道部最近活動積極
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我真的覺得可惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  他們兩個今年根本沒參加過比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們真的還是劍道部的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師出去做什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在怎麼說也不會被解雇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  咱們現在正做得火熱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好還會批預算下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹬鼻子上臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才算數？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！段君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候學會抽胴的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陪小都都練習的時候慢慢就記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為重心比較低  所以能比較平穩地打出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會也要告訴小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑  勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  還有幾天時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦  你考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要我考慮什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了誰建立的部團啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹劍23話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好評應援中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝指導
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～完啦完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果宮崎同學還是沒趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們等下留一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  老師你要借錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們回去吧  今天不用打掃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你掛在這裡啊  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說  因為他們兩個要我們中止活動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整一年？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不同意！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:13:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？為什麼大家都在努力  卻還要受這樣的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為學校這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太奇怪了！根本是蠻不講理！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  這已經決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山和岩佐  自春天開始就沒有參加過正式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習比賽也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們已經算退部的話  就和劍道部沒有關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有發過退部書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  就算不發也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  要甩掉他們對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說謊對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  就可以說服校方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他們的處分也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也不會抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…這樣決定真的好嗎？老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要決定的人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你  紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們的部團活動的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你這個部長來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是顧問嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部團活動是你們學生的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來向學校傳達你們覺得最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天之前回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要中止活動…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是甩掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭你們轉告一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你還是有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都看著小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠最近變了  好像變回原樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得像沒有加入部團之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我原本就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  家裡還有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！發動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都…做不好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎？你怎麼在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到處找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為見不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  說謊是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為輸給了凱莉  所以覺得練習很痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！都已經那樣在練習了還是不能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼練到能贏不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一起回部團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我新學會了抽胴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭也教給小都都啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎你這種有才能做什麼都一帆風順的人不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有拼上性命練習也做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠也戰勝不了的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我練劍道還有什麼意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山他…就沒做過什麼像樣的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也從來沒打掃過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光會欺負女生做些有的沒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話…我覺得就算沒他才更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩佐也從來都是見死不救的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的男生都退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽的時候甚至都不來為我們加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是他們自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道會這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠他們入部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山他們不來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的覺得部團活動太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這話很刺耳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實講我不想管他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一來氣氛一下就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  慢慢習慣這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後變得不再看他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有一定要讓小珠他們這些一年生出賽的這個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕走他們兩人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是騙人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你今天變得好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君也這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方變了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來  就好像急於取勝一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…慢悠悠的話就會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時放下手裡的劍怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來  自從你懂事起一直都在練劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身手和心靈都是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有必要勉強繼續劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我和你媽媽都不願意看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
